{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-haiku-4-5-20251001","id":"msg_014WtHqqejPM7ubpX1R7Nfqp","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01TiuJ1prtyD8XrEXQdHZE4H","name":"Write","input":{"file_path":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/tools/title-loop/input/Carrot and Ginger Soup.generated.22.txt","content":"CARROT AND GINGER SOUP\n\nThis warming soup has been a staple in my kitchen for years, especially during the\ncolder months when fresh ginger is abundant at the market. The natural sweetness of\nthe carrots combines beautifully with the sharp, bright notes of ginger and a whisper\nof orange zest. I often make this in large batches and freeze portions for quick\nweeknight dinners. It's equally delicious served hot or chilled as a summer appetizer.\n\nIngredients:\n- 2 lbs carrots, peeled and chopped\n- 1 medium onion, diced\n- 3-inch piece fresh ginger, peeled and sliced\n- 4 cups vegetable stock (or chicken stock)\n- ½ cup heavy cream (or coconut milk)\n- 2 tablespoons olive oil\n- Zest and juice of 1 orange\n- Salt and white pepper to taste\n- Fresh cilantro for garnish\n- Toasted caraway seeds (optional)\n\nPreparation:\n1. Heat oil in large pot over medium heat\n2. Sauté onion until translucent, about 4-5 minutes\n3. Add carrot pieces and ginger slices\n4. Cook 8-10 minutes, stirring occasionally\n5. Pour in stock and bring to simmer\n6. Cook 25-30 minutes until carrots very tender\n7. Remove ginger slices\n8. Blend soup in batches until smooth (or use immersion blender)\n9. Return to pot and stir in cream\n10. Season with salt, pepper, orange zest and juice\n11. Simmer gently for 5 minutes\n12. Serve hot with cilantro and caraway seeds\n"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":8,"cache_creation_input_tokens":614,"cache_read_input_tokens":93215,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":614},"output_tokens":1,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8392c7b6-a894-479d-8452-f4cbd3d27103","uuid":"5f710f26-5117-477b-b385-4cbdfffafdc8"}
